<div style="font-size:90%">
<br><br>

<b>2013 June 15:&nbsp;&nbsp;   Bagtikan dojo ceases operations</b><br><br><br>


A renovation project of our landlord at our Bagtikan dojo has obliged us to move out of our space in the Doña Guadalupe Bldg. on Bagtikan Street, San Antonio Village, Makati.<br><br>

Consequently, as of 2013 June 15, our Bagtikan dojo will cease operations indefinitely. We will be searching for a new home for our branch dojo and will let everyone know when we are ready to reopen the branch.<br><br>

UPDATE: A fire gutted the 6th floor of our erstwhile Bagtikan venue last Thursday, July 11th. Fortunately, no one in the building was hurt, and most of our tatami system components had previously been relocated to another floor, and were thus not damaged in the fire.<br><br>

<br>


